      <title>Slow Cookers: Why Every Home Needs a Slow Cooker</title>
      <link>http://www.ovalslowcookers.co.uk/slow-cooker-advice-tips/slow-cookers-home-slow-cooker/</link>
      <comments>http://www.ovalslowcookers.co.uk/slow-cooker-advice-tips/slow-cookers-home-slow-cooker/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Jan 2010 11:01:57 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>ovalslowcookers</dc:creator>
