Before I had a slow cooker, making stock was a drawn out process involving lots of boiling on the stove &amp;#8211; it [...]&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.ovalslowcookers.co.uk/best-slow-cooker-recipes/slow-cooking-making-the-perfect-chicken-stock/"&gt;Slow Cooking: Making the Perfect Chicken Stock&lt;/a&gt; is a post from: &lt;a href="http://www.ovalslowcookers.co.uk"&gt;Oval Slow Cookers&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;



