      <description>Slow cooking has few rules but here are some pointers for slow cooking success in Part 1 of my Slow Cooking Tips series.
Using Liquid in the Slow Cooker
Don&amp;#8217;t forget to include some liquid in your slow cooker. You need to include some liquid in your slow cooker to start off the process of slow cooking. [...]&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.ovalslowcookers.co.uk/slow-cooker-advice-tips/slow-cooking-tips-part-1/"&gt;Slow Cooking Tips &amp;#8211; Part 1&lt;/a&gt; is a post from: &lt;a href="http://www.ovalslowcookers.co.uk"&gt;Oval Slow Cookers&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;



